'Grayscale Investments, the world’s largest digital asset manager, has filed to register five new trusts for cryptocurrency assets' - Monero included!
Grayscale has registered trust filings for five new assets: Aave, Cosmos, Polkadot, Monero and Cardano, but the company says product launches are not yet certain.  https://t.co/Vnk0MgPHnF

Grayscale has now incorporated five more trusts, including those tied to Polkadot $DOT, Aave $AAVE, Monero $XMR and Cardano $ADA.  Last Thursday they incorporated six trusts tied to $LINK, $XTZ, $BAT, $MANA, and $FIL  https://t.co/G76fbpF7u8  https://t.co/ODpLuQ1u6Y
